{"tid":1249490,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"當你真心愛過一個人 每逢夜晚都總會諗起佢","createTime":"2019-06-21T17:39:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T16:56:03.000Z","uid":134300,"like":72,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6f25b2620462da85b75e5b32a8d57dda29f654bc","tid":1249490,"uid":134300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:39:55.000Z","msg":"我知你有上連登，或者你會睇到呢個post<br />\n<br />\n你教識左我咩係愛，但卻離開左我，亦唔比我再愛你<br />\n曾經應承過你嘅一切，最終都無法實現<br />\n而家我剩低嘅就只有遺憾同失落<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲可以留言同我傾下？"},{"pid":"7985608dcfb3fcea06dfa4c4835e3e7ac52d5daf","tid":1249490,"uid":154447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:56:28.000Z","msg":"隔左幾耐？"},{"pid":"b0980160d5a125af5d423c21388d22b792c4fec8","tid":1249490,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:59:20.000Z","msg":"Sorly 我已經唔記得咗你"},{"pid":"0168d91d7818d2d2fd84dd94fb5a757d7dd7078a","tid":1249490,"uid":134300,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7985608dcfb3fcea06dfa4c4835e3e7ac52d5daf","tid":1249490,"uid":154447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:56:28.000Z","msg":"隔左幾耐？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T19:14:44.000Z","msg":"幾日前正式分手"},{"pid":"a6b5a3836102f7072fd30ba6922a604e7cee4482","tid":1249490,"uid":178574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T19:16:12.000Z","msg":"咁你講下咩為之愛？"},{"pid":"ad3fa3bcf9ac1f2c0a849e5a81bb0674c14ca276","tid":1249490,"uid":17299,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T20:02:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b99733171472d2d580b497cd00f6eaec9073707","tid":1249490,"uid":119401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T20:24:56.000Z","msg":"諗起咪好囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5060573ba6586a825b107c03921d34aa7ef896","tid":1249490,"uid":29848,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T20:29:52.000Z","msg":"見到佢鍾意既野 會諗起佢<br />\n但隨之而來既係失落"},{"pid":"533fff7860fef4c052223d818f7c661c420f0cf6","tid":1249490,"uid":29540,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T20:30:32.000Z","msg":"當真正願意愛一個人 沒法再愛更需要恨"},{"pid":"d393bff5ef925b8eaba5ee8dcbf74c50bd57c44f","tid":1249490,"uid":228436,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T21:27:26.000Z","msg":"當真係遇到一個自己愛過嘅人，就算分開咗都會無啦啦ff如果仲一齊嘅日子，所有事都好想繼續一齊做，唔只係夜晚，係分分秒秒都諗緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cda10ef20f7269bfa888cd53b599822f7d88afd7","tid":1249490,"uid":133501,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T21:29:29.000Z","msg":"我差唔多兩年都係咁，日日都會諗起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb95765e07927e05150db58266bac62ad34e1857","tid":1249490,"uid":160130,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T22:17:50.000Z","msg":"做乜都會諗起佢&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n然後諗起佢嗰陣，就乜都唔想做&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n然後呢種感覺不停不停循環<br />\n成件行屍走肉咁<br />\n<br />\n喊唔出噏住又傷<br />\n喊得出個心又痛<br />\n<br />\n一日loop十幾二十次真係人都癲&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"a41471428cc6c23a5b2d90f992c81be54d42fd42","tid":1249490,"uid":102154,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T03:18:47.000Z","msg":"我都成日諗起一個女仔<br />\n<br />\n佢係我舊公司的同事黎<br />\n<br />\n果陣雖然同一間公司 但唔同工作地方<br />\n<br />\n有一段時間係同一個地方的<br />\n<br />\n但無耐 佢辭職了<br />\n<br />\n唉 後悔佢走果陣無問佢拎電話 keep contact.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"474ada32d756f0736501e6a6f5596d36b6b9c049","tid":1249490,"uid":134300,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T07:51:38.000Z","msg":"以前有好多歌都聽唔明，例如月球上的人、綿綿<br />\n但而家每次聽到都會明白當中果種哀傷<br />\n<br />\n上面有位巴打問咁咩係愛<br />\n或者我咁講未必有好多人認同<br />\n但我覺得所謂愛就係將對方嘅快樂睇得比自己更重<br />\n<br />\n其實或者愛佢，我就更應該放手<br />\n因為佢認為我已經比唔到幸福佢<br />\n<br />\n共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55b6623c02b99569845283a4b0d985816531a829","tid":1249490,"uid":20126,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"474ada32d756f0736501e6a6f5596d36b6b9c049","tid":1249490,"uid":134300,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T07:51:38.000Z","msg":"以前有好多歌都聽唔明，例如月球上的人、綿綿<br />\n但而家每次聽到都會明白當中果種哀傷<br />\n<br />\n上面有位巴打問咁咩係愛<br />\n或者我咁講未必有好多人認同<br />\n但我覺得所謂愛就係將對方嘅快樂睇得比自己更重<br />\n<br />\n其實或者愛佢，我就更應該放手<br />\n因為佢認為我已經比唔到幸福佢<br />\n<br />\n共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T08:47:13.000Z","msg":"到此為止... <br />\n&quot;無道理的對罵是年紀小的不智&quot;<br />\n<br />\n好撚掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想回到過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"277d16fea64457f2bba55b93841c7d70f482666a","tid":1249490,"uid":237809,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T09:00:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2998ab7e35f31ff64bf68f74c2627f4497cdd8e4","tid":1249490,"uid":251404,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T11:22:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f38ed5f73d1a8fd648618abdcb007c58bbba590","tid":1249490,"uid":55019,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2998ab7e35f31ff64bf68f74c2627f4497cdd8e4","tid":1249490,"uid":251404,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T11:22:11.000Z","msg":"